Funny as hell. My husband and I saw this comedy show on cable and I just had to track it down and buy it. We have watched this comedy dvd so many times that I'm surprised it hasn't melted in the dvd player. We also put it on during family gatherings and have let family/friends borrow it but we had to stop doing this because people do not want to return it. if you need a good laugh this is the dvd to buy.
